--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
10 BSE Financial Services Stocks Hit 52-Week Highs Despite Sensex Drop
On Wednesday, the benchmark Sensex fell by around 386 points, settling at 81,715. Despite the overall market drop, 10 stocks from the BSE Financial Services index hit their 52-week highs, reaching their peak levels over the past year. Such breakouts are generally seen by traders and investors as bullish indicators, suggesting strong upward momentum and the potential for continued gains.
